London.title: Viet Food
London.text: Authentic Vietnamese cuisine! The staff were really nice and fast with the orders. I really liked all the dishes and enjoyed the ambience. I went with one friend so I didn’t book in advance and we had no issues. It was Saturday around 14:30.

London.author: testing
London.title: Copita
London.text: A beautiful selection of dishes! Really quick and friendly service. The layout of the restaurant was intimate and welcoming and the food was delicious. My favourite was the scallops, first time I’d ever tried them but definitely not the last 😌 next time, we’ll sit outside!
